```py
.product {
    /* apply padding and margin */  
    padding: 10px;
    margin: 10px;
    /* apply border */
     border: 1px solid #ccc;
    /* apply border radius */
     border-radius: 5px; 
    /* apply background color */
     background-color: #fff; 
    /* apply box shadow */
     box-shadow: 0 0 5px #ccc; 
    /* apply display */
    display: inline-block; 
    /* apply width */
     width: 200px; 
    /* apply text align */
     text-align: center; 
    /* apply text decoration */
     text-decoration: none; 
    /* apply color */
     color: #333;  
} 
```

